<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_ncmc_epic.EncryptHelper</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>false</client_callable><description/><name>EncryptHelper</name><script><![CDATA[var EncryptHelper = Class.create();
EncryptHelper.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {},
    hexToAscii: function(hexValue) {
        var hex = hexValue.toString();
        var str = '';
        for (var n = 0; n < hex.length; n += 2) {
            str += String.fromCharCode(parseInt(hex.substr(n, 2), 16));
        }
        return str;
    },
    type: 'EncryptHelper'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>CCMC-03</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2021-07-09 17:12:49</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>ff959d781b19741054cea9f6b04bcb8f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>EncryptHelper</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Epic Integrations" source="x_ncmc_epic">aeb251341bd5741054cea9f6b04bcbbf</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Epic Integrations">aeb251341bd5741054cea9f6b04bcbbf</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_ff959d781b19741054cea9f6b04bcb8f</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>CCMC-03</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-07-09 17:12:49</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
